videos.description: Jake Browning throws an interception on the opening drive, giving Oregon great field position.
videos.headline: Oregon intercepts Browning on opening drive

videos.description: Salvon Ahmed takes the end around and scampers for a 25-yard touchdown to give Washington the lead.
videos.headline: Quick end-around catches Oregon off guard for Washington TD

videos.description: Justin Herbert throws a 12-yard pass to Dillon Mitchell who zigs and zags for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Oregon's Herbert throws 12-yard TD

videos.description: Washington head coach Chris Peterson dials up a reverse pass to set up his Huskies deep in Oregon territory.
videos.headline: Washington dials up trick play on 33-yard completion

videos.description: Salvon Ahmed finds the corner for a 2-yard touchdown run to give Washington a 17-10 lead.
videos.headline: Ahmed's second rushing TD gives Washington lead

videos.description: Justin Herbert fires a bullet to Jaylon Redd who tip-toes the sideline for a ridiculous 9-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Oregon's Redd walks tight rope for 9-yard TD

videos.description: The Ducks and Huskies exchanged touchdowns in an exciting first half in Eugene.

videos.headline: Oregon, Washington score 17 apiece in wild half

videos.description: CJ Verdell pushes his way up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Oregon's Verdell shoves his way in for 6

videos.description: Jake Browning escapes the pocket and throws a deep pass to Ty Jones for a 43-yard touchdown to tie Oregon.
videos.headline: Washington ties it with long Browning pass

videos.description: Jake Browning gives Washington a big first down on a key fourth-down completion to Sean McGrew.
videos.headline: Browning converts big fourth-down pass

videos.description: Washington's Peyton Henry misses a 37-yard field goal at the end of regulation to send the game to overtime.
videos.headline: Washington misses game-winning FG

videos.description: Washington settles for a field goal in overtime's first possession against Oregon.
videos.headline: Washington opens OT with FG

videos.description: Oregon overcomes stands by Washington for a 30-27 win in overtime behind CJ Verdell rushing for 111 yards and two TDs, including the winning score.
